                        <handDesc>
                            <handNote scope="sole" xml:id="hand-1">
                                <p>The main text was copied in small-format <term type="script">mixed minuscule</term> 
                                    with many majuscule letters, ligatures and inclusions, 
                                    in dark brown ink and with dense text distribution. Accents are small and modestly executed; 
                                    ascenders and descenders are restrained within the line but more prominent in the outer margins.</p>
                            </handNote>
                        </handDesc>

